description: Try our easy to follow Peach Eton Mess recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Eton mess,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Low salt,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Quick & easy dessert,Stone fruit,Christmas,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Peanut free
name: Peach Eton Mess Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 825g can peaches sliced in juice, drained

recipeInstructions.text: Place pure cream and vanilla bean paste in a bowl and beat, using an electric mixer, until soft peaks form. Add double cream and gently whisk until combined and soft peaks form (do not overwhisk).
Layer meringues, cream mixture and peaches onto a serving plate. Drizzle with passionfruit pulp and garnish with mint.
